@node P5 "help.LIBRARY?"
@toc "main"

I know, I know...   System libraries aren't usually huge text files
describing AmigaDOS commands, but I just couldn't think of any other
name.

An individual who sent me a Three Stooges postcard asked if AHelp
could be done without the AHelp.library.  The answer: currenlty no.
But stay tuned to future versions!

@endnode

